PLACE Barilla(R) Pronto(TM) pasta, garlic, onions, bell pepper, beans, tomatoes, and spices into the pot. ADD broth/water. Cook over high heat. After 5 minutes ADD the spinach. Continue cooking until all of the liquid is absorbed and the spinach is wilted, stirring occasionally (5-10 minutes). STIR in cheese while the chili mac is warm. TOP with fresh parsley and serve!